snippet.title: Super Mario Land 2 + Wario's Conquest // SAGE 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/super-mario-land-2-warios-conquest-sage-24-demo.2190/
or
https://gamejolt.com/games/SML2WCremake/895658

After a crusade against the mysterious alien Tatanga in Sarasa Land, Mario decided to return back to his own island for a well earned rest. Turns out an evil creep who goes by the name of Wario took the chance of his abscence to take over Mario's castle and put the people of Mario Land under a magic spell! To reclaim his castle and free Mario Land from its new ruler, Mario must find the 6 Golden Coins scattered across the island and invade ...his own home?!

Developed by Yak0
